location.fullValue: Julian Plan, The Springs at Skyline Trails

data.description:
This home is a 3 bed /2 bath/ 2 car garage & is conveniently located in the Mustang School District close to I-40,shopping, restaurants and parks. It's only a 15 mile commute to OKC!
Built by Ideal homes, this house has a clean, elegant feel & includes an extended patio w/ a vaulted pergola, perfect for backyard enjoyment! 
It features spacious rooms, open concept layout, Large Walk in Pantry, an extra 2' length in the garage then the standard models, gas range, Quartz Countertops, tile backsplash and breakfast bar!
*VA Assumable Loan w/ 3.125% interest* Ask how you can qualify!
Principal & Interest payment $711.48
